\fB\-\-isolation\fP=""
    Container isolation technology

.PP
\fB\-\-kernel\-memory\fP=0
    Kernel memory limit

.PP
\fB\-l\fP, \fB\-\-label\fP=
    Set meta data on a container

.PP
\fB\-\-label\-file\fP=
    Read in a line delimited file of labels

.PP
\fB\-\-link\fP=
    Add link to another container

.PP
\fB\-\-link\-local\-ip\fP=
    Container IPv4/IPv6 link\-local addresses

.PP
